dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:20:06.000Z","msg":"唔知你咩budget 玩咩game 手汗多唔多<br />\n不過我推無線充電板嘅滑鼠<br />\nLogitech Corsair Razer <br />\n都有出用依類滑鼠 <br />\n其他兩個牌子我唔清楚<br />\n我自己就用開Logitech G703 <br />\n不過如果你手汗多的話 我建議你可以買Pro wireless<br />\n因為Pro wireless 用硬膠 比較適合有手汗<br />\n所以總括而言都係睇返你budget 手大細 流唔流手汗<br />\n<br />\n就算budget 唔夠買無線充電mouse pad 都好<br />\n我都建議買無線滑鼠 用過返唔到轉頭<br />\n無線滑鼠充滿100%電都起碼用24小時以上<br />\n所以每次用完再插返條線就得<br />\n<br />\n最後 可以參考下依篇野 同埋裡面個網<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=60030&amp;snB=2073560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D60030%26snB%3D2073560&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4wHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=65b5f845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=60030&amp;snB=2073560</a>"},{"pid":"e49f2f6c86986eedf3ddefd32b84749138befe91","tid":1195264,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:23:57.000Z","msg":"Corsair_Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf38b8144b35a408b3acb5dc603e7d196f0f117","tid":1195264,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"Filco FTW"}]}